{
  "stem": "26983.11",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 24.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember his speech, when he said-- because at that time, they knew the war is going slowly to the end-- when the war-- when the German-- oh, sorry-- when the Russian will be five kilometers from here, I will take my knife, he would say, [GERMAN], he was--",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A hairdresser.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of you, I will kill you until your Jewish blood will be sprinkling here on the wall.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And terrible speeches.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the second.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also the block was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German criminals.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know only [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The second name, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew it-- and I own knew that he was lynched after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we have been in this block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But even in this block-- of course, what happened when we came, we went again through [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took everything we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember I was very, very clever, and even from Auschwitz, I managed to smuggle a box with cigarettes, some 20 cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was in my shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How old were you at that time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was barely 15.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I smuggled the cigarettes and I somehow was able to bring some to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And AT Mauthausen I managed to change it for a special, I don't know--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two or three rations of soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Mauthausen, there were many ration, and POVs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were treated in the most cruel way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes the German led them naked and pour on them cold-- I mean water they were frozen to death and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember there was a little--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surely, 10, 15 under.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, there were Czech, non Jews, prisoners, political prisoners, who behaved most wonderfully to us, and they let us have their ration of soup.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
